OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772294630
OL,3,CElderly pedestrian killed by HGV in M1
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FA elderly pedestrian has been killed
OL,7,Fafter being hit by a HGV on a motorway
OL,8,Fin Barnsley.
OL,10,FPolice said an "elderly man" had been
OL,11,Fstruck by a white DAF Trucks HGV on
OL,12,Fthe southbound carriageway of the M1
OL,13,Fat junction 37.
OL,15,FThe incident happened at around 2:15am
OL,16,Fon Saturday morning - the man died at
OL,17,Fthe scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
