OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772294630
OL,3,CElderly pedestrian killed by HGV in M1
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the force said
OL,7,Fidentification was not yet confirmed
OL,8,Fas officers were trying to establish
OL,9,Fnext of kin.
OL,11,F"Officers and the ambulance service
OL,12,Fattended, but despite the best efforts
OL,13,Fof emergency services, the pedestrian,
OL,14,Fan elderly man, sadly died at the
OL,15,Fscene.
OL,17,F"Whilst identification is not yet
OL,18,Fconfirmed officers are making
OL,19,Fenquiries with who we believe to be
OL,20,Fthe next of kin."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
