OL,3,CElderly pedestrian killed by HGV in M1
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police are appealing
OL,7,Ffor ant witnesses or anyone who saw
OL,8,Fthe man before the collision, either
OL,9,Fon Dodworth Road or the southbound
OL,10,Fentry slip road, to come forward.
